name: Web Ventures Group
overview: Web Ventures Group is the developer behind the SEO campaign management solution, seocrates. SEOCRATES offers a unique solution for managing a company’s link building efforts and utilizing what the company refers to as “compounded link building” to help give your link building efforts more weight.
